        "text": "Most standalone pools run $375 to $475 for a first inspection and Form 23 certificate. Larger properties with multiple gates, shared pools, or jobs that need a re-inspection inside the 90-day rectification window sit between $475 and $650 depending on travel and complexity."
      }
    }
  ]
